title: Melbourne manhunt after female jogger was grabbed from behind, sexually assaulted - Yahoo7
text:
Manhunt after female jogger sexually assaulted Mel Buttigieg - Yahoo7 News on February 9, 2017, 11:24 am Manhunt after female jogger was grabbed from behind, sexually assaulted, in Melbourne Share Melbourne manhunt after female jogger was grabbed from behind, sexually assaulted - Yahoo7 Police are searching for a man who sexually assaulted a 31-year-old woman jogging in Melbourne on Saturday night. 
The woman was running along the foreshore at the inner-city suburb of Middle Park around 11 to 11.30pm when she was grabbed from behind by an unknown man, police said. 
She was forced face down into the sand and sexually assaulted at Beaconsfield Parade, between Fraser and Langridge streets. 
A man and a woman came to the victimâ€™s aid, along with two other men wearing white shirts, after her attacker fled the scene.
